And the feet over on this side represent social

00:09:36.680 --> 00:09:40.660
psychology. Social psychology is a psychology
of how people interact with each other; the

00:09:40.660 --> 00:09:43.080
psychology of our social interactions.

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:48.050
The feet on this side is cognitive psychology.
Cognitive psychology is psychology of the

00:09:48.050 --> 00:09:49.510
