not only to make speculations about behavior

00:10:36.850 --> 00:10:40.680
being unconscious but to trace what parts
of the brain are responsible for conscious

00:10:40.680 --> 00:10:43.440
and unconscious behavior and how they interact
with each other.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:47.190
