00:42:33.049 --> 00:42:40.440
methodology, you might judge the data by the
weight that that particular data should hold,

00:42:40.440 --> 00:42:45.940
in other words, is that factor that you're
testing very important? But what your unconscious

00:42:45.940 --> 00:42:51.190
mind does is it adjusts the weight that you
give to data and it adjusts your view of the

00:42:51.190 --> 00:42:57.119
