00:43:10.739 --> 00:43:14.809
to tend to support that conclusion. And it's
very important this unconscious 'cause if

00:43:14.809 --> 00:43:18.930
you try to consciously do it you're too smart
for that, you're gonna know that I'm just

00:43:18.930 --> 00:43:23.410
fooling myself. But your unconscious can fool
you in a way that you're not aware of and

00:43:23.410 --> 00:43:25.209
